B.W8=new A.o([B.e,"Advancing computing knowledge through world-class research, innovative education, and meaningful impact across Africa and beyond.",B.f,"Ons bevorder rekenaarkennis deur w\xeareldklas-navorsing, innoverende onderwys en betekenisvolle impak oor Afrika en verder.",B.h,"Siqhubela phambili ulwazi lweekhompyutha ngophando olukumgangatho ophezulu, imfundo entsha, kunye nefuthe elilandelekayo kuyo yonke iAfrika nangaphaya."],t.O)
